{"tid":909192,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[小生意] 外國人付款/郵寄問題","createTime":"2018-11-20T07:47:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T07:47:26.000Z","uid":82542,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"94b743e7b0052f1d52be3ab8ebb4cd425864c955","tid":909192,"uid":82542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:47:26.000Z","msg":"本身有係IG SHOP賣開野<br />\n<br />\n眼見其他人賣比外國人 自己又想試下<br />\n想問收錢方面 用咩收?<br />\n自己見到有人用Paypal收錢<br />\n但如果買家話收唔到貨就可以退錢<br />\n咁姐係寄野方面要用掛號 運費都HKD幾十蚊<br />\n但見到人地international shipping 都係USD 2<br />\n<br />\n有無其他付款工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}